      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TICKET CONFETTI (2) broke from the inside draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only 1.5 lengths (22.56) behind Black Statesman at this track. Has a win and two minor placings from three starts from this draw. Sure to be about the mark. MAC AND CHEESE (1) started big odds in far stiffer grade latest when finishing 4th over 400m at Geelong. Was a Geelong winner in lesser company the start prior. Should be thereabouts. BLANKET GAME (4) turned in a moderate performance last time when fifth at Horsham over 410m behind Paw Qwerty (23.75) in a Grade 5. Key player if finds best. ASTON CURRENCY (6) picked up a cheque out of this box most recently - in the mix again.",
